detail.name: Piccolo
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, then reveal up to 1 <Gotenks> or Extra and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: ピッコロ
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、「ゴテンクス」かエクストラ1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
